        <p>I reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting to this page. Your continued use of the site following any changes indicates your acceptance of the new terms.</p>

        <h2>7. Contact Information</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions regarding these Terms of Service, please contact me at: <a href="mailto:zeeshan.haider28@gmail.com">zeeshan.haider28@gmail.com</a></p>
